# Laravel IDE Helper

## When to use

- Generating autocompletion files for Laravel facades, models, and meta
- Configuring barryvdh/laravel-ide-helper in a project
- Setting up composer scripts for automatic IDE helper regeneration
- Fixing missing PHPDoc annotations on Eloquent models

## Keywords

`ide-helper`, `barryvdh/laravel-ide-helper`, `ide-helper:generate`, `ide-helper:model`, `ide-helper:meta`, `autocompletion`, `PHPDoc`, `_ide_helper.php`
